-- South Africa's Afrisam proposes merger with rival PPC 
-- By Tiisetso Motsoeneng
-- Wed Dec 10, 2014 06:33AM EST
-- None



JOHANNESBURG, Dec 10 (Reuters) - South African cement maker PPC <PPCJ.J> has received a merger proposal from unlisted rival Afrisam Group, the company said on Wednesday.

PPC said in a statement its board was considering the non-binding proposal and it would make further announcements in due course.